#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:2 1f8f4d9455fb425a873d4c12a655d6bb
msgid "开源硬件-小安派系列"
msgstr "Open-Source Hardware - AiPi Series"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:16 880d2b2df73645dcaa7c5b2b3f5eef18
msgid "小安派开发板能驱动60pin的屏幕吗"
msgstr "Can the AiPi development board drive a 60-pin screen?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:17 e92f4d1f16bf45afb550e49ae5bd8641
msgid "不能，开发板内部没有这么多引脚接到屏幕上"
msgstr "No. The development board does not have enough internal pins connected to the screen."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:20 48f8a0b6bd714ea6a551d39beb81b74b
msgid "小安派开发板的屏幕和摄像头能同时使用吗"
msgstr "Can the screen and camera of the AiPi development board be used at the same time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:21 13e0017b07854061bf3e130374a834b5
msgid "不能同时使用，因为这两个外设都占用一些相同的引脚，同时使用会导致外设无法正常工作"
msgstr "No, they cannot be used at the same time, because these two peripherals occupy some of the same pins. Using them simultaneously will cause the peripherals to fail to work properly."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:24 debd25267b2c490dbeb62692c1a62f0b
msgid "小安派-Eyes开发板有语音识别功能吗"
msgstr "Does the AiPi-Eyes development board have voice recognition?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/Ai-pi/index.rst:25 f1b2db9d3a3040f98d561ec5f20f6fbd
msgid "没有，目前该板子没有集成语音识别功能"
msgstr "No. Currently, this board does not integrate voice recognition."
